Nancy, this is Constanza Fuentes.
Nancy, 这位是Constanza Fuentes.

5
00:00:55,500 --> 00:00:56,631
Constanza, my wife Nancy.
Constanza, 这是我妻子Nancy.

6
00:00:56,680 --> 00:00:58,282
I am so pleased to meet you.
认识你很高兴.

7
00:00:58,300 --> 00:00:59,845
Listen, let's go upstairs. 
我说, 咱们上楼吧.

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,354
I'd love to show you around.
我带你们到处看看.

9
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:09,366
Is it Nancy Hobart, 
你是叫Nancy Hobart, 

10
00:01:09,390 --> 00:01:10,790
or did you keep your own name?
还是姓你娘家的姓?

11
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,470
It's Hobart.
我姓Hobart. 

12
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:13,327
I took Richard's name when we got married.
我和Richard结婚时就改随他的姓了.

13
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:15,438
Oh, I took my husband's name, too.
Oh, 我也是姓我丈夫的姓.

14
00:01:15,600 --> 00:01:17,187
But that was a long time ago.
不过那是很久以前的传统了.

15
00:01:17,700 --> 00:01:19,258
These days, many women don't.
如今, 很多女性都不改随夫姓了.

16
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:23,321
