我们结婚那会儿, 要是不改随夫姓的话会很麻烦的.

17
00:01:23,340 --> 00:01:26,265
So we gave mine to our daughter as a middle name.
不过我女儿的中间名用的是我的姓.

18
00:01:26,300 --> 00:01:27,743
Your daughter is Beth, right?
你女儿叫Beth, 对吧?

19
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:29,772
Elizabeth Jane Ellis Hobart.
Elizabeth Jane Ellis Hobart.

20
00:01:29,780 --> 00:01:30,864
Oh, it's beautiful.
Oh, 这名宇真好听.

21
00:01:30,870 --> 00:01:32,779
It sounds like an author's name, doesn't it?
听上去像是作家的名字, 对吗?

22
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,806
