A minor celebrity.
我是说有点儿小名气的人.

33
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,244
Oh, no, Nancy. 
Oh, 不, Nancy. 

34
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:57,890
If we are going to have a celebrity, 
我们要是想让他做名人的话, 

35
00:01:57,900 --> 00:01:58,985
let's do it in a big way.
